description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'Cardio Workout At Home - 30 Min Aerobic Exercise' from the channel Roberta's Gym.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: This 30-Minute cardio workout can easily be done at home. Cardio workouts are helpful because they help burn much more calories in less time.

This in turn gives you good weight loss results, a healthier heart and a better circulation.

For better fat loss results you should do this workout 4-5 days per week.

Do the workout and don't forget to subscribe to the channel and receive workout videos regularly: each Monday. Wednesday and Friday!
